# corpora/ datasets — git tracking policy.
#
# The SEDRA IV JSON cache (sedra_cache/api/{word,lexeme,root}/*.json) and the
# SEDRA 3 words.json are committed to this repo for reproducibility (see commit
# "neural: add SEDRA IV cache to repo"). SEDRA is license-restricted: academic/
# personal use, no redistribution of altered versions, cite Kiraz (see
# corpora.SEDRA_CITATION). Observe those terms if you redistribute.
#
# Excluded from git: the large derived SQLite database (~112 MB; rebuild with
# `-m corpora.sedra_db`), transient scraper temp files, and OS/editor noise.
sedra_cache/sedra.db
*.tmp
.DS_Store

# Python noise
__pycache__/
